text: TCDD DE36000 are a series of diesel-electric locomotives used by the Turkish State Railways and that are produced by TÜLOMSAŞ in Eskişehir, Turkey under licence from GE. ==External links== * Trains of Turkey page on DE36000 Category:General Electric locomotives Category:Co-Co locomotives Category:Turkish State Railways diesel locomotives Category:Standard gauge locomotives of Turkey Category:Railway locomotives introduced in 2014
